<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .options {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .option-card {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem;
            width: 300px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        .option-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        .option-card h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .option-card p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .option-card .icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .free-prompt {
            border-top: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        }
        .character-builder {
            border-top: 4px solid #2196F3;
        }
        .background-remover {
            border-top: 4px solid #FF9800;
        }
        .ollama-api {
            border-top: 4px solid #9C27B0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .free-prompt .button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
        }
        .character-builder .button {
            background-color: #2196F3;
        }
        .background-remover .button {
            background-color: #FF9800;
        }
        .ollama-api .button {
            background-color: #9C27B0;
        }
        .button:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>ComfyUI Image Generator</h1>
        <div class="options">
            <a href="/free-prompt" class="option-card free-prompt">
                <div class="icon">‚úèÔ∏è</div>
                <h2>Free Prompt</h2>
                <p>Write your own custom prompt and generate images with complete creative freedom.</p>
                <span class="button">Start Creating</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/prompt-builder" class="option-card character-builder">
                <div class="icon">üë§</div>
                <h2>Character Builder</h2>
                <p>Create detailed character prompts using our structured builder with predefined options.</p>
                <span class="button">Build Character</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/remove-background" class="option-card background-remover">
                <div class="icon">‚úÇÔ∏è</div>
                <h2>Remove Background</h2>
                <p>Upload an image and remove its background automatically using AI.</p>
                <span class="button">Remove Background</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/ollama-test" class="option-card ollama-api">
                <div class="icon">ü§ñ</div>
                <h2>Ollama API</h2>
                <p>Test and interact with the Ollama API using different models and prompts.</p>
                <span class="button">Test API</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/config" class="option-card config">
                <div class="icon">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
                <h2>Configuration</h2>
                <p>Configure and test API endpoints for ComfyUI and Ollama.</p>
                <span class="button">Configure</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 